These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, lily, daffodil
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, rat
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person who growsamaryllis and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Flower   | daffodil | lily | amaryllis |
| Pet           | ferret  | rat     | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, electronic, reggae
There 3 different types of food: lemon, eggplant, apricot
1. the person eating lemon is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of country is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the person eating eggplant##7
3. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | country | reggae |
| Food     | eggplant       | apricot     | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, water
House: art-deco, futuristic, wooden
1. the futuristic house is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the art-deco house##7
2. the wooden house is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | coffee | mirinda | water  |
| House   | wooden  | futuristic  | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, weightlifting, skiing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, comedy, time-travel
1. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the person who's sport is weightlifting##7
2. the person watching comedy movies is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Sport           | weightlifting | surfing | skiing     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | action          | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, red, fuchsia
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person who likes red##7
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Color   | brown      | fuchsia     | red   |
| Transport     | skateboard | quad-bike | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, singing, skydiving
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, pakistani
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
2. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the pakistani and the person who's hobby is gardening##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby   | skydiving    | singing     | gardening     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | japanese | colombian |

