.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
House: craftsman, townhouse, cottage
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the craftsman house and the person who's sport is badminton##7
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| House     | cottage       | townhouse      | craftsman       |
| Sport   | badminton | skateboarding | basketball |

