There 3 different types of food: plum, apple, avocado
1. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the doctor##3
2. the person eating plum is somewhere between the person eating avocado and the electrician##7
3. the person eating apple is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | entrepreneur | doctor  | electrician |
| Food   | avocado      | plum | apple      |

