.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
3 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, go
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, manager, teacher
1. the teacher is not the person playing go##6
2. the manager is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the doctor is somewhere between the manager and the person playing mah-jongg##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | go | poker   |
| Job     | teacher    | doctor  | manager |

