.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, sprite
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, dancing, writing
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is dancing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk   | sprite    | coffee |
| Hobby      | writing | hiking | dancing |

