.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, snowboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is handball##7
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | traveling | fishing | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | snowboarding    | volleyball    | handball         |

