2. the person eating potato is the person eating potato##1
3. the person eating peach is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person driving the scooter##7
4. the person driving the scooter is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato | peach     | avocado   |
| Transport   | bus   | bike | scooter |

