.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, tea
City: berlin, edinburgh, new-york
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person traveling to edinburgh##7
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | tea     | almond-milk |
| City        | new-york | berlin | edinburgh    |

 